==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: immobilization
<hw>immobilization</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The act or process of limiting movement or making incapable of
movement; <as>as, <ex>immobilization</ex> of the injured knee was
necessary; the storm caused complete <ex>immobilization</ex> of the
rescue team</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> immobilizing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immobility</ent>⟦br⟧
